# ValuTime

ValuTime is an innovative iOS app designed for freelancers and professionals who want to track every second of their time while assigning a monetary value to it. Whether you're working on hourly projects, fixed-cost engagements, or simply tracking leisure activities, ValuTime helps you understand how every moment contributes to your overall productivity and financial goals.

## Table of Contents

- [Overview](#overview)
- [Features](#features)
- [Architecture & Technology](#architecture--technology)
- [Installation](#installation)
- [Usage](#usage)
- [Development & Testing](#development--testing)
- [Future Enhancements](#future-enhancements)
- [License](#license)

## Overview

ValuTime combines time tracking with real-time financial calculations to offer:

- **Live Earnings**: See your current earnings as you work, based on an assigned hourly rate.
- **Project Analysis**: Compare planned vs. actual time for fixed-cost projects to evaluate effective hourly rates.
- **Holistic Time Logging**: Track both work and non-work activities (like leisure, sleep, gym, etc.) to get a comprehensive view of your daily routine.

Built using Xcode and SwiftUI, ValuTime is designed to deliver a seamless, intuitive experience while running efficiently in the background on iOS.

## Features

### Activity Tracking:

- Easily switch between different activity modes (work, leisure, sleep, gym, etc.).
- Option to track precise time intervals (per second or minute) for detailed analytics.

### Financial Integration:

- Real-time display of earnings during hourly projects.
- Calculation of effective hourly rates for fixed-cost projects.
- Opportunity cost estimation for non-billable activities.

### User Interface & Dashboard:

- Clean, minimalist design with clear visual cues (color coding and icons).
- Central dashboard summarizing daily, weekly, and project-specific stats.
- Graphs and reports to visualize time distribution and productivity trends.

### Data Management & Privacy:

- Local data storage using Core Data with provisions for future cloud syncing.
- Emphasis on user privacy and secure data handling.

### Background Processing:

- Intelligent background task handling to ensure continuous time tracking without draining battery life.

## Architecture & Technology

- **Platform**: iOS
- **Programming Language**: Swift
- **UI Framework**: SwiftUI
- **Data Storage**: Core Data (with potential for cloud integration)
- **Background Processing**: Utilizing iOS background tasks and notifications for continuous tracking

## Installation

To run ValuTime on your iOS device, follow these steps:

1. Clone the Repository:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/valuTime.git
cd valuTime
```

2. Open the Project in Xcode:

- Open ValuTime.xcodeproj or ValuTime.xcworkspace in Xcode.

3. Build and Run:

- Select your target device (or simulator) and press Cmd + R to build and run the app.

## Usage

### Initial Setup:

- Upon first launch, configure your hourly rate and default activity categories.

### Tracking Time:

- Use the main dashboard to start and stop timers for different activities.
- Switch modes as you transition between work and non-work tasks.

### View Analytics:

- Access detailed summaries and graphs from the dashboard to see how your time translates into monetary value.
- Review project-specific reports to compare planned vs. actual time expenditure.

## Development & Testing

### Development:

- The project is built using Xcode with SwiftUI. Utilize Combine and other Swift frameworks for managing state and background tasks.

### Testing:

- Use Xcode's simulator for initial testing.
- Implement unit tests and UI tests to ensure accurate time tracking and data management.
- Consider using TestFlight for beta testing and gathering user feedback.

## Future Enhancements

### Advanced Automation:

- Automatic detection of activity transitions via integration with calendars and location data.

### Expanded Platform Support:

- Plans for expanding to other platforms or integrating with wearable devices.

### Enhanced Analytics:

- Deeper insights and recommendations based on historical time tracking data.

### Cloud Syncing:

- Enable secure data syncing across multiple devices.

